<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,1615,1786]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,267,1615,1641]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Chikatunov, V. &amp; Pavlicek, T." box="[276,627,1615,1641]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" pagination="37 - 65" refId="ref6815" refString="Chikatunov, V. &amp; Pavlicek, T. (1997) Catalogue of the beetles (Coleoptera) in Israel and adjacent areas: 1. Scarabaeoidea. Klapalekiana, 33, 37 - 65." type="journal article" year="1997">Chikatunov &amp; Pavlíček (1997)</bibRefCitation>
recorded 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Chikatunov &amp; Pavlicek" authorityYear="1997" box="[744,907,1615,1641]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Aplidia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="baudii">
<emphasis box="[744,907,1615,1641]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">Aplidia baudii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[980,1081,1615,1641]" name="Lebanon" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">Lebanon</collectingCountry>
, after 
<bibRefCitation author="El-Hariri, G." box="[1154,1342,1615,1641]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" refId="ref6997" refString="El-Hariri, G. (1971) A list of recorded insect fauna of Syria. Vol. 2. University of Aleppo, Faculty of Agriculture, Aleppo, 306 pp." type="book" year="1971">El-Hariri (1971)</bibRefCitation>
, and reminded old records from 
<collectingCountry box="[437,500,1651,1677]" name="Syria" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">Syria</collectingCountry>
. This species was described from 
<collectingCountry box="[884,965,1651,1677]" name="Cyprus" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">Cyprus</collectingCountry>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Baraud, J." box="[1020,1182,1651,1677]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" pagination="539 - 580" refId="ref6524" refString="Baraud, J. (1988) Contribution a l'etude du genre Haplidia Hope (Coleoptera Scarabaeoidea Melolonthidae). Revue Suisse de Zoologie, 95, 539 - 580. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 79672" type="journal article" year="1988">Baraud (1988)</bibRefCitation>
recorded it from Rhodos. 
<bibRefCitation author="Bezdek, A." box="[204,370,1687,1714]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" pagination="249 - 280" refId="ref6643" refString="Bezdek, A. (2016) Rhizotrogini. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Volume 3. Scarabaeoidea, Scirtoidea, Dascilloidea, Buprestoidea, Byrrhoidea. Revised and updated edition. Brill, Leiden, Boston, pp. 249 - 280." type="book chapter" year="2016">Bezděk (2016)</bibRefCitation>
did not give credit to the records of this species from the continent. 
<bibRefCitation author="Miessen, G." box="[1131,1306,1687,1714]" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" pagination="57 - 73" refId="ref7539" refString="Miessen, G. (2016) Essais sur le genre Aplidia Hope 1837 a Chypre et commentaires sur quelques especes limitrophes (Coleoptera, Scarabaeoidea, Melolonthidae, Rhizotrogini). Entomologie Faunistique-Faunistic Entomology, 69, 57 - 73." type="journal article" year="2016">Miessen (2016)</bibRefCitation>
and Sehnal (in press), consider the synonymy between 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kraatz" authorityYear="1882" box="[633,810,1723,1749]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="baudii">
<emphasis box="[633,810,1723,1749]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">Haplidia baudii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<collectingCountry box="[824,909,1723,1749]" name="Cyprus" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">Cyprus</collectingCountry>
, 
<emphasis box="[920,1048,1723,1749]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">patria falsa</emphasis>
) and 
<taxonomicName authority="Burmeister, 1855" authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1855" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="544" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirticollis">
<emphasis box="[1111,1326,1723,1749]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">Haplidia hirticollis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Burmeister, H. C. C." pageId="8" pageNumber="544" refId="ref6743" refString="Burmeister, H. C. C. (1855) Handbuch der Entomologie. Vierter Band. Besondere Entomologie. Fortsetzung. Zweite Abtheilung. Coleoptera Lamellicornia Phyllophaga chaenochela. Theod. Chr. Friedr. Enslin, Berlin, x + 569 pp." type="book" year="1855">Burmeister, 1855</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, from southern 
<collectingCountry box="[428,481,1759,1785]" name="Italy" pageId="8" pageNumber="544">Italy</collectingCountry>
. This species does not belong to the Lebanese fauna.
</paragraph>
